  "title": {
    "zh": "破风板与侧箱气流",
    "en": "Bargeboards and sidepod airflow"
  },
  "summary": {
    "zh": "前轮甩出的乱流要由破风板重新整理，再交给「可乐瓶」侧箱与底板边缘去管理。破风板与侧箱造型是 2010 年代各队气动的「签名」，2022 年更催生三种截然不同的侧箱流派。",
    "en": "The dirty air thrown by the front tyres is reorganised by bargeboards, then handed to the 'Coke-bottle' sidepods and floor edges. These were teams' aero 'signature' in the 2010s; 2022 spawned three distinct sidepod schools."
  },
  "sourceIds": ["source-book-f1-illustrated-engineering"],
  "updatedAt": "2026-07-14T12:00:00.000Z",
